(28, 1, '2018-02-27 01:21:33', '2018-02-27 06:21:33', '<strong>THE SIERRA MADRE MOUNTAIN RESORT AND HOTEL</strong>\r\n\r\nShare ko lang mga lodi, ang ganda kasi ng place para hindi mapansin. <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f4f/1/16/1f601.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😁</span></span> Since malapit na Holidays! <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fce/1/16/1f600.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😀</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fac/1/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">📌</span></span> Just 1hr and 30mins trip from the Metro. Swak na swak na sa day-off niyo bes para hindi ka na mapunta pa sa malayong lugar para lang mag-unwind.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fac/1/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">📌</span></span> Mala-Tagaytay and Baguio ang feels mga bes! Sobrang lawak ng lugar, maraming pwedeng puntahan. Lakad lakad ka lang, makakalimutan mo na mga problema at heartbreaks mo! <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f4f/1/16/1f601.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😁</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fac/1/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">📌</span></span> Murang mura na mga bes! 50 pesos lang ang Entrance for Viewing, kung gusto mo naman magswimming 200 pesos lang din Entrance. At eto pa, kung overnight kayo libre na ang Entrance mga bes, bale Room Rates lang ang babayaran niyo which is mura na din. Magaganda naman mga room, pangmaramihan talaga. <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/ffb/1/16/263a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">☺</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fac/1/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">📌</span></span> Maraming mga outdoor activities mga bes! Picnic, camping, obstacle courses, jungle trails, trekking, ziplines, swimming at may Natural Falls din (free na rin)!\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fac/1/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">📌</span></span> Pang-team building, pang-family bonding, pang-barkada outing, pang-honeymoon at pwede rin magwalwal with friends! <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fd0/1/16/1f602.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😂</span></span>\r\n\r\nHOW TO GET THERE:\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fe4/1/16/270f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">✏</span></span> From Cubao, sakay kayo ng FX or Jeep going to Cogeo. Mabilis lang byahe bes, depende sa traffic. P40/person lang ang pamasahe kapag FX bes. Ewan ko sa Jeep baka mas mura. <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f4f/1/16/1f601.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😁</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fe4/1/16/270f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">✏</span></span> Kapag nasa Cogeo na kayo, hanapin niyo lang yung terminal ng jeep papuntang Sampaloc (Brgy yun sa Tanay, Rizal). <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fce/1/16/1f600.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😀</span></span> P55/person lang pamasahe bes\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fe4/1/16/270f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">✏</span></span> Sabihin niyo sa driver na pakibaba kayo sa The Sierra Madre Mountain Resort. <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f4f/1/16/1f601.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😁</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fe4/1/16/270f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">✏</span></span> 1 hour lang biyahe mga bes. Wag mainip. <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f4f/1/16/1f601.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">😁</span></span>\r\n\r\nENJOY!\r\n\r\n* Kapag pauwi na kayo bes, either sakay kayo papuntang Sampaloc Terminal or hintay lang kayo ng jeep sa harap ng resort. Dapat naghihintay na kayo ng 5pm mga bes kasi til 6pm lang ang mga jeep. <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f7b/1/16/1f68e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">🚎</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fea/1/16/1f695.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">🚕</span></span>\r\n\r\n** Tig 1K lang nagastos namin bes, apat kaming workmates. Kasama na room rates, pamasahe at foods (dinner, bfast at lunch). <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f2a/1/16/1f354.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">🍔</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f5a/1/16/1f35d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">🍝</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f66/1/16/1f372.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-20\" src=\"http://blog.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-21\" src=\"http://blog.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-22\" src=\"http://blog.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-23\" src=\"http://blog.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-27\" src=\"http://blog.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />', 'THE SIERRA MADRE MOUNTAIN RESORT AND HOTEL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-27 01:21:33', '2018-02-27 06:21:33', '', 19, 'http://blog.localhost/2018/02/27/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
